               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Dāwit “Psalter” (fols. 1r-158vb)
 I-1) Mazmura Dāwit “Psalms of
                     David” (fols. 1r-122v)
 I-2) Maḥālǝya nabiyāt “The Canticles of the
                     Prophets” (fols. 123r-136r)
 I-3) Maḥālǝya maḥālǝy “Song of Songs” (fols.
                     136r-143v)
 I-4) Wǝddāse Māryām “The Praise of Mary” (fols.
                     144ra-154vb)
 I-5) ʾAnqaṣa bǝrhān “The Gate of Light” (fols.
                     154vb-158vb).</summary>
